
```gitignore
## Build results
bin/
obj/
out/

## User-specific files
*.user
*.rsuser
*.suo
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates

## Visual Studio / VS Code / Rider
.vs/
.vscode/
.idea/

## NuGet
*.nupkg
packages/
!**/packages/build/
*.nuget.props
*.nuget.targets

## Logs
*.log

## Environment / Secrets
appsettings.Development.json
appsettings.Local.json
.env
.env.*

## ASP.NET Core Scaffolding
ScaffoldingReadMe.txt

## Entity Framework
*.dbmdl
*.jfm

## Publish Output
publish/
wwwroot/dist/

## Node modules (if frontend inside same repo)
node_modules/

## OS generated files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Test Results
TestResults/
*.trx
*.coverage
*.coveragexml

## JetBrains Rider
_ReSharper*/
*.DotSettings.user

## Azure / Deployment
*.PublishSettings
```
